</treatmentCitation>
, Farr &amp; Zijlstra (1996+), 
<treatmentCitation author="Smith, G. F. &amp; Figueiredo, E." box="[944,1324,194,221]" page="169" pageId="2" pageNumber="89" year="2018">
<bibRefCitation author="Smith, G. F. &amp; Figueiredo, E." box="[944,1324,194,221]" pageId="2" pageNumber="89" pagination="162 - 172" refId="ref7466" refString="Smith, G. F. &amp; Figueiredo, E. (2018 a) The infrageneric classification and nomenclature of Kalanchoe Adans. (Crassulaceae), with special reference to the southern African species. Bradleya 36: 162 - 172. https: // doi. org / 10.25223 / brad. n 36.2018. a 10" type="journal article" year="2018">Smith &amp; Figueiredo (2018a: 169)</bibRefCitation>
